data.description: Located at the end of a dead end street, this spacious property is Move In Ready! This home features 5 bedrooms, 2 1/2 bathrooms, and a large main floor living room with a large picture window where you can enjoy all of your family time. The 2 car garage has tons of room for extra storage. If you need to find a spot to park your camper/RV, look no further than this property which features RV parking. Enjoy entertaining outdoors? Look no further than this property! The backyard is an absolute dream with a large covered patio and beautiful trees where you can pick your own fruit. The basement is ready for you to make it all your own and just needs some tape, texture and paint. Call to see today!
